title: How-To: Make the Easiest Homemade Chicken Pot Pie
description:
It's winter, it's cold, and there's one thing you need to eat: chicken pot pie. Farideh Sadeghin, Culinary Director of MUNCHIES, has you covered. The MUNCHIES recipe has everything you would want out of a traditional pot pie, except for the fact that ours is topped with flaky biscuits. If your plans include wearing sweatpants and watching tv, this is the meal for you.

Check out the recipe here: https://munchies.vice.com/en_us/article/4x5emj/biscuit-topped-chicken-pot-pie
